{"tid":777134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[借古鑑今] 香港同乾隆年代係好撚相似","createTime":"2018-08-12T15:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T07:13:35.000Z","uid":199211,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f72b496c3cdc2795aeeb7d99e53e193e1885bd49","tid":777134,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:53:12.000Z","msg":"大家可能聽過清朝康雍乾盛世 覺得三位都係好皇帝 但要論功績 乾隆只係個貪威識食既超級二世祖 同前兩位無得比 然而佢統治期間竟然同香港有幾分相似 大家不妨引以為鑑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我分幾個point 大家睇得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.食老本<br />\n所謂乾隆盛世完全係靠康熙（啊爺）同 雍正（老豆）打落既江山 佢死好命 有祖蔭護佑 繼承左大好江山 唔似得其他好皇帝要收拾先帝既爛攤子 努力一番先開創到盛世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港擁有既優勢 不論法律 經濟 教育 制度 文化 等等好大程度上都係英國所賜 無英國香港根本乜都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n2.敗家<br />\n乾隆好大喜功 經常晒錢做啲不利民生既事 出兵打仗 (但只係打啲廢鳩部落小國） 封自己做十全老人 極度要面 加上佢六下江南 每次都好大陣仗 原來豐盈既國庫都俾佢敗撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港同理 好撚多大白象工程 起完都唔見得有用 有咁既財力做其他野好過<br />\n<br />\n3.官吏腐敗<br />\n係人都知乾隆重用和珅 佢貪既錢竟然係朝廷十幾年既收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上行下效 下面既人唔見得會幾廉潔<br />\n香港既貪就打開新聞都見唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4.老人政治<br />\n乾隆真係唔知點解好撚有福氣 25歲登基做到85歲之後讓位俾嘉慶 自己就做左幾年太上皇 但佢讓位只係當初發誓在位時間唔超過啊爺康熙既60年（可能佢自己都估唔到自己咁長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )  做皇帝咁爽當然唔會想退落嚟 於是佢讓位不讓權 有睇TVB 天命都知 佢做太上皇仍然手攬大權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘉慶頭幾年可以話係傀儡皇帝 乜都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  乾隆可謂老人政治既表表者<br />\n香港無論政治定各方面都係old seafood 揸fit 後生無任何話事權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想上位可謂難若登天<br />\n<br />\n5. 後知後覺<br />\n英國佬一直想同中國做生意 所以派使者馬甘尼嚟一探究竟 <br />\n乾隆一直覺得中國係天朝上國 英國只係蠻夷 不屑同英國佬做生意 唔撚開放關口 事實上英國已經有工業革命 國力開始同始同清朝有距離 同你正經往來你唔肯 唯有同武力打鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後諗住搞洋務運動都太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人或有或有都一種驕傲既心理 (我都有少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 畢竟香港都風光過 但其實唔少地方都超越左我地 有啲產業唔推行遲啲人地唔侵我地玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係要有啲警覺下<br />\nbtw乾隆係清朝最後一個盛世 之後啲皇帝都俾人打到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我希望香港唔會行條咁既舊路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁多 再講驚俾人屌我踩港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f1a9ca2a8016f7340af872e0ccfc5fe53b8d2c","tid":777134,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"講起又講 係英國有心栽培香港 定係香港無意中學到？"},{"pid":"6aa57e46bd4c2a177871f8c6ea987bdb72f4ca61","tid":777134,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f1a9ca2a8016f7340af872e0ccfc5fe53b8d2c","tid":777134,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"講起又講 係英國有心栽培香港 定係香港無意中學到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"應該都有心既 初時貪香港個地理位置好 後尾經濟彈上去簡直係生金蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋後期都放權 俾香港人做官 林鄭 薯片都係受惠者嚟既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3073a3ea2770f68abda4df7782626d720afa32","tid":777134,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:06:43.000Z","msg":"草民一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3138a254c0f71a1c4afbe0376035cfeeccf9c2","tid":777134,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:07:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d645404d57e805476c384786b488a03654cf2ebb","tid":777134,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"草民二推"},{"pid":"bcb69433a09d93c1904c0f0c0e94aaf55984dddd","tid":777134,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b134bbdd5d8fefe9d0b65163d77d82c713c12ba3","tid":777134,"uid":195918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"請繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e413a63e2a3e36b1ee22fac02948563e533323","tid":777134,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"奶波魔巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1313b861ca09d75ffd14aa29ccf842fdcdc1ed","tid":777134,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b134bbdd5d8fefe9d0b65163d77d82c713c12ba3","tid":777134,"uid":195918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201